definition: Taiwan pr. used in 夾生|夹生[jia1 sheng1] and 夾竹桃|夹竹桃[jia1 zhu2 tao2]

sentences.english: Browse to a folder other than the workspace.
sentences.chinese: 瀏覽至資料夾而非工作區。

sentences.english: Allows unsubscribing of mail folders in the folder tree context menu.
sentences.chinese: 允許在資料夾樹的快顯選單中取消訂閱郵件資料夾。

sentences.english: Allows unsubscribing of mail folders in the folder tree context menu.
sentences.chinese: 允許在資料夾樹的快顯選單中取消訂閱郵件資料夾。

sentences.english: Locks on folders are implicitly recursive.
sentences.chinese: 資料夾的鎖定是隱含遞迴。

sentences.english: The Styles Library folder identifies where the program stores project-specific styles definitions.
sentences.chinese: 資料夾可識別程式儲存專案特定的型式定義的位置。

sentences.english: Select whether you want to store the messages in this folder as one file per message (maildir) or as one big file (mbox).
sentences.chinese: 請選擇在這個資料夾中要用什麼格式儲存信件。

sentences.english: You cannot copy this trash folder.
sentences.chinese: 您不可以將回收筒資料夾複製。

sentences.english: Files and folders can only be moved into the trash.
sentences.chinese: 只有檔案跟資料夾能移到回收筒中。

sentences.english: Middle-click on the main icon opens the folder.
sentences.chinese: 對主圖示點擊滑鼠中鍵會開啓該資料夾。

sentences.english: Deploy the document-level solution to a shared folder on your network.
sentences.chinese: 將文件層級方案部署至網路上的共用資料夾。

sentences.english: Folder where copies of the handheld databases are kept.
sentences.chinese: 掌上型裝置中的資料庫要複製到哪個資料夾。
打開資料夾與習俗亞洲漿紙。

sentences.english: A folder named "%B" already exists. Do you want to replace it?
sentences.chinese: 名爲“%B”的資料夾已經存在。要取代它嗎？

sentences.english: To add a new folder, right-click on blank area and click Add a new folder.
sentences.chinese: 於樹狀圖右鍵選單中，點擊新增資料夾。

sentences.english: Add the folder of this file to the source folder list.
sentences.chinese: 新增此檔案所在的資料夾到程式源碼資料夾清單中。

sentences.english: Add the folder of this file to the source folder list.
sentences.chinese: 新增此檔案所在的資料夾到程式源碼資料夾清單中。
